Episodes 1-12



Type: TV Series, 12 episodes


Rick lives on the island of Windaria, inhabited by various races such as elves and beast-people. Amnesiac, he is rescued by Airy, Amil, and Neris, and starts to work at their bakery. But when the red moon rises and the deathly wind blows, they are all overwhelmed by a series of strange events.
